Installation (Ubuntu):

    git clone git://github.com/ajw/dotvim.git ~/.vim

Installation (Windows):

    git clone git://github.com/ajw/dotvim.git C:\Documents and Settings\wildea\vimfiles
    cp .vimrc ../_vimrc
    cp .gvimrc ../_gvimrc

Create symlinks:

    ln -s ~/.vim/vimrc ~/.vimrc
    ln -s ~/.vim/gvimrc ~/.gvimrc

Switch to the `~/.vim` directory, and fetch submodules:

    cd ~/.vim
    git submodule init
    git submodule updatetest
